**Summary:** This documentation describes the Amplitude to Extole event streaming destination integration that sends real-time user behavior events from Amplitude to Extole's Customer-Led Growth platform to trigger advocacy campaigns, refer-a-friend programs, and customer activation initiatives. The integration requires mapping Amplitude user_id to email addresses in Extole and uses access tokens for authentication.

